==English==

===Etymology===
from the name ''[[Gymnospermae]]''

===Noun===
'''gymnosperms'''

# {{botany}} A group of [[seed plants]], whose [[seed]]s are not enclosed in an [[ovary]]. The most important group of gymnosperms (''[[Gymnospermae]]'') are the [[conifers]] (''[[Coniferae]]'' or ''[[Coniferales]]'').

